===Etymology===
[[atheism]] from {{Gr.}} ''[[αθεός]] (Atheós) "without god".

===Noun===
{{en-noun-unc}}
# The claim that no God or gods exist.
# The absence of belief in [[deity|deities]]. (weak atheism)

